}}</ref>

==反应和应用==
吡啶-2-甲醛可以用于合成[[氯解磷定|氯解磷定]]药物。

[[醛基|醛基]][[官能团|官能团]]可作为亲核进攻的试剂，制备[[Schiff碱|Schiff碱]]，用作双齿配体。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Chatterjeea, D. |author2=Mitra, A. | title = Synthesis, Characterization and Reactivities of Schiff-base Complexes of Ruthenium(III)| journal = [[J._Coord._Chem.|J. Coord. Chem.]] | volume = 57 | pages = 175–182 | year = 2004 | doi = 10.1080/00958970410001662435}}</ref>亚氨基吡啶的配合物十分稳定。<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.1175313 | title = White Phosphorus is Air-Stable Within a Self-Assembled Tetrahedral Capsule | year = 2009 | last1 = Mal | first1 = P. | last2 = Breiner | first2 = B. | last3 = Rissanen | first3 = K. | last4 = Nitschke | first4 = J. R. | journal = Science | volume = 324 | issue = 5935 | pages = 1697–1699 | pmid = 19556504}}</ref>

